data.description: Immaculate executive style home in the highly sought-after Waterside section of Lake Forest! Boasting a spacious and light-filled floorplan with newly refinished hardwoods, this stunning home offers a very unique floorplan- highly coveted and rarely found in the community! The main level features a formal office with french doors for privacy, full bathroom, grand formal dining room that seats 12+, a large fireside family room with views to the beautiful backyard, and a gorgeous updated white kitchen with views to the oversized keeping room with second fireplace! Step outside to a lovely screened-in porch that overlooks the level, fenced yard, providing the perfect spot for relaxation and entertainment. Ascending upstairs, there are 3 huge secondary bedrooms with walk-in closets and hardwood flooring plus the oversized owner’s suite which features a large flex space/sitting area and a huge private balcony that offers captivating mountain views and seasonal lake views. The remodeled master bathroom is a true oasis, featuring slate herringbone flooring, a modern soaking tub, quartz counters, oversized tile and quartz shower and his and hers closets! The finished basement is ready for enjoyment, with a bedroom, bathroom, entertainment area, and home gym plus extra storage space. This home is perfectly situated in the community, nestled between two cul-de-sacs and on a large fenced corner lot. The subdivision offers an array of community amenities, including a community dock on a 40 acre lake with fishing and boating opportunities, tennis and pickleball courts, a volleyball sand court, basketball courts, a playground, and a resort-style clubhouse and pool and seasonal swim team! Top rated schools and minutes from the new Cumming City Center!
